# Lesser 404 redirects — Netlify reads this file automatically.
# We point visitors landing on dead/expected URLs to the closest live
# destination instead of a 404 page. 302 for short-term redirects we
# may turn into real routes later (cart, search, account, login);
# 301 for ones we don't plan to build separately (shipping, returns,
# wholesale, press).
/cart       /shop        302
/search     /shop        302
/account    /shop        302
/login      /shop        302
/shipping   /faq         301
/returns    /faq         301
/wholesale  /distributor 301
/press      /contact     301
